high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Pick the cup up from under the coffee maker.
Turn to the left and face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and turn it on and then open the microwave and take the cup out.
Turn to the right and face the coffee machine.
Put the cup under the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug under a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and walk through the kitchen to the coffee machine on the counter
Pick up the white mug from the coffee machine
Turn left and face toward the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave and remove it
Turn right and face back toward the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Move to the coffee pot to the right of the microwave.
Pick up the mug from the pot.
Turn left to the microwave.
Put the coffee mug inside and heat it before removing it and closing the door.
Turn right to the coffee pot.
Place the mug on the coffee pot.
anns.task_desc: Return the heated mug to the coffee pot.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the wall, turn right, move to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the heated mug to the coffee machine on the left.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the coffee machine on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the coffee mug that is in the coffee machine.
Turn left to face the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and place the coffee mug inside, then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the door and remove the coffee mug then close the door.
Turn right to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Place the heated coffee mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated coffee mug in the coffee machine.

take the cup from the coffee machine

open the microwave door and put the cup in the microwave and close the door and turn on the microwave and when finished open the door and take out the cup and close the door
